#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "⚠️ Sensitive Content Notice"
msgstr "⚠️ Isaziso somxholo onobuzaza"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This module includes content that may be sensitive. You can check it out by yourself first. This will prepare you well for sharing the content with your teen and others afterwards.\n"
"\n"
"If you need support, see the “Support Contacts” section in your Library for help."
msgstr ""
"Esi sifundo siquka umxholo ongabanobuthathaka. Ungazikhangelela ngokunokwakho kuqala. Lonto ingakulungiselela kakuhle ukwabelana nomxholo nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kunye nabanye emva koko.\n"
"\n"
"Ukuba udinga inkxaso, jonga kwicandelo \"Uqhagamshelwano lwenkxaso\" kwithala leencwadi ukuze uncedakale."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today’s topic is about teen safety.\n"
"\n"
"Teens can spend a lot of time outside the house or online, where it is harder for us to keep them safe. Talking together about safe and unsafe places — and how to prevent problems — really helps."
msgstr ""
"Abantwana abafikisayo bangachitha ixesha elininzi ngaphandle kwendlu okanye kwi-intanethi, apho kunzima ukuba sibagcine bekhuselekile. \n"
"\n"
"Ukuthetha kunye ngeendawo ezikhuselekileyo nezingakhuselekanga, nendlela yokuthintela iingxaki, kunceda ngokwenene."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why is teen safety important for you and your family?"
msgstr "Kutheni ukhuseleko lwabantwana bakho abafikisayo lubalulekile kuwe nosapho lwakho?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today our topic is teen safety \n"
"\n"
"It is our responsibility as parents to try to keep our teens safe and help them to keep themselves safe. An important part of that is that we are all aware of the safe and unsafe areas in our communities.\n"
"\n"
"It is also our responsibility to ensure that they understand the dangers that they might be exposed to when they are online. That way our teenagers will be responsible and be able to make right decisions to keep themselves safe too."
msgstr ""
"Molweni, kuni nonke. \n"
"\n"
"Umxholo wethu wanamhlanje umalunga nokhuseleko \n"
"\n"
"Kuluxanduva lwethu njengabazali ukuzama ukugcina abantwana bethu abafikisayo bekhuselekile kwaye sibancede nabo bazigcine bekhuselekile. Indawo ebalulekileyo apho kukuba sonke sazi indawo ezikhuselekileyo nezingakhuselekanga kwiindawo esihlala kuzo. \n"
"\n"
"Ikwaluxanduva lwethu ukuqinisekisa ukuba bayaziqonda iingozi abaziveza kuzo xa bekwi-intanethi. Ngalo ndlela abantwana bethu abafikisayo baya kukwazi uthatha uxanduva kwaye ibenze lonto bakwazi ukwenza izigqibo ezizizo ukuze bazigcine bekhuselekile nabo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Sometimes our teens notice things about their surroundings that we don’t. By talking and listening, we can better understand their world and guide them through challenges – including the risks they face online.\n"
"\n"
"With our support, they can learn to stay safe and make good decisions. \n"
"\n"
"This guidance is important for both girls and boys. Abuse can happen in different ways — including sexual abuse."
msgstr ""
"Ngamanye amaxesha abantwana bethu abafikisayo baqaphela izinto ezisingqongileyo thina esingaziboniyo. Ngokuthetha nangokumamela, singaliqonda ngcono ihlabathi labo kwaye sibakhokhele kwimiceli mngeni – kuquka imingcipheko abajongene nayo kwi intanethi.\n"
"\n"
"Ngenxaso yethu, bangafunda ukuhlala bekhuselekile kwaye benze izigqibo ezifanelekileyo.\n"
"\n"
"Esi sikhokelo sibalulekile kubo bobabini, amantombi kunye namakhwenkwe. Ukuhlukememza kunganceda ngendlela uzahlukeneyo - kuquka ukuhlukunyezwa ngezesondo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "_Child sexual abuse can happen in different ways. It can happen when someone touches a child in a sexual way, makes sexual comments or requests, pressures or forces a child, or offers money or gifts to ask for sexual things. It can happen face-to-face or online._"
msgstr "_Ukuhlukunyezwa kwabantwana ngezesondo kungenzeka ngendlela uzahlukeneyo. Ingenzeka xana umntu ebamba umntwana ngendlela yesondo, ephawula ngendlela yesondo okanye ecela, exinezela okanye enyanzela umntwana, okanye enikela ngemali okanye izipho ukucela izinto zesondo. Ingenzeka bejongene okanye kwi intanethi._"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A safety plan helped @data.characters.media_female_8.name protect her teen. Tap play to hear more"
msgstr "Isicwangciso sokhuseleko sisebenzile ku@data.characters.media_female_8.name ukukhusela umntwana wakhe ofikisayo. Cofa udlala umamele nangakumbi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I was so grateful to make the safety plan with my teen. I thought I knew which areas are safe for my teen and which are not. But when we made the safety plan together, I realised that my girl knew more areas that I was not aware of.\n"
"\n"
"I also thought she was safe at school, but through this activity I realised she was being bullied and the teachers did not do anything about it.\n"
"\n"
"The more we talked, the more I understood and got information from my teen. That really helped me to protect my teen and keep her safe."
msgstr ""
"Ndibe nombulelo omkhulu ukwenza isicwangciso sokhuseleko nomntwana wam ofikisayo. Bendicinga ndiyazazi indawo ezikhuselekileyo zomntwana wam ofikisayo nkunye nezingalunganga. Kodwa xa besisenza izicwangciso zokhuseleko kunye, Ndiye ndaqonda ukuba intombi yam yazi indawo ezininzi kunoba ndisazi.\n"
"\n"
"Bendisoloko ndicinga ukuba ukhuselekile esikolweni, kodwa ngalomsebenzi ndiye ndaqonda ukuba uyaxhatshazwa kwaye abafundisi ntsapho abenzinto ngalonto.\n"
"\n"
"Ngokuya sithetha, ngokuya ndiqonda kwaye ndafumana inkcukacha kubantwana bam abafikisayo. Ngokwenene lonto indincedile ukukhusela umntwana wam ofikisayo kwaye ndimgcine ekhuselekile."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"The most important way to help keep your teen safe is to make sure that they know they can talk to you about anything. \n"
"\n"
"Work with your teen to notice risks — like when someone pressures or makes them feel uncomfortable, online or offline.\n"
"\n"
"**Let’s look at examples of risky situations to help you spot warning signs.**"
msgstr ""
"Eyona ndlela ibalulekileyo yokunceda umntana wakho ofikisayo ahlale ekhuselekile kukuqinisekisa ukuba bayayazi ukuba bangathetha nawe malunga ngayo nantoni na.\n"
"\n"
"Sebenzisana nomntana wakho ofikisayo ukuqaphela imingcipheko - efana naxa umntu emcinizelela okanye emenza azive engakhululekanga, kwi-intanethi okanye ngaphandle kwe intanethi.\n"
"\n"
"**Masijonge imizekelo yeemeko ezinomngcipheko ukukunceda ubone iimpawu ezilumkisayo.**"

