"Indoda:"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Does not listen to @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name"
msgstr "Akammameli u @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yells and calls @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name names"
msgstr "Ukhwaza kwaye abize amagama ka @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "May touch @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name without permission"
msgstr "Ingambamba u @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name ngaphandle kwemvume"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Pressures @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name"
msgstr "Ifaka u @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name phantsi koxinzelelo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Makes @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name feel unsafe"
msgstr "Imenze u @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name azive engakhuselekanga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes, all of these are warning signs! Your ‘no’ should always be respected.\n"
"\n"
"Also remember, if people at home or outside use alcohol and other drugs this can be a warning sign, as those can make people angry, aggressive, and even violent."
msgstr ""
"Ewe, zonke eziimpawu zezilumkiso! U 'hayi' wakho makasoloko ehloniphekile.\n"
"\n"
"Kwaye khumbula, ukuba abantu ekhaya okanye ngaphandle basebenzisa utywala okanye ezinye iziyobisi nalena ingaba luphawu, jengokuba zingabenza abantu babenomsindo, babe ndlongondlongo kwaye babenobundlobongela."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"To keep our teens safe, we need to understand the dangerous situations they could get into! \n"
"\n"
"Let’s get practical now, and draw a map of safe and unsafe places. You can include: \n"
"- 🗺️ Places from your community\n"
"- 🌐 Apps/websites you use online"
msgstr ""
"Ukugcina abantwana bethu abafikisayo bekhuselekile, kufuneka siqonde iimeko eziyingozi abanokungena kuzo!\n"
"\n"
"Makhe senze ngoku, kwaye sizobe iimephu ezimbini zeendawo ezikhuselekileyo neziyingozi:\n"
"- 🗺️ Iindawo hlala kuyo\n"
"- 🌐 I-App/iiwebhsayithi oyisebenzisayo kwi intanethi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you make this map together with your family now?"
msgstr "Ungakwazi ukwenza le mephu kunye nosapho lwakho ngoku?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, my family can join in now"
msgstr "Ewe, usapho lwam lungazibandakanya ngoku"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let me try it out by myself"
msgstr "Makhe ndiyizame ngoku ngokwam"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Great! You will need a:\n"
"\n"
"- 📄 Piece of paper (or old newspaper or a cardboard box) \n"
"- 🖊️ Pen"
msgstr ""
"Kulungile! Uza kudinga i:\n"
"\n"
"- 📄 Phetshana elincinci (okanye iphephandaba elidala okanye ibhokisi yekhalibhodi) \n"
"- 🖊️ Usiba"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 1: Draw all the important places in your community."
msgstr "Inyathelo 1: Zoba zonke indawo ezibalulekileyo kwindawo ohlala kuyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Draw a map of your teen’s community, with pictures of all the main places like streets, your house, school, shops, places your teen visits.\n"
"\n"
"Remember to include your phone and other internet devices, as mobile apps and websites are also places where you and your teen can spend a lot of time!"
msgstr ""
"Zoba imephu yokuhlala yomntwana wakho ofikisayo, enemifanekiso yazo zonke iindawo eziphambili njengezitrato, indlu yakho, isikolo, iivenkile, iindawo ezindwendwelwa ngabantwana bakho abafikisayo.\n"
"\n"
"Khumbula ukubandakanya ifowuni yakho kunye nezinye izixhobo ze-intanethi, njengee-apps eziphathwayo kunye neewebhusayithi zikwayindawo apho wena nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ninokuchitha ixesha elininzi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 2: Choose which places are safe and unsafe."
msgstr "Inyathelo 2: Khetha indawo ezikhuselekileyo nezingakhuselekanga."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"- Which areas on your map are safe for teenagers? CIRCLE these\n"
"- Which areas on your map are unsafe for teenagers? CROSS those off\n"
"- What makes a place safe or unsafe? Is this different for boys and girls? \n"
"- Looking at the places you mapped out, what rules could you come up with together to help your teen stay safe?"
msgstr ""
"- Zeziphi iindawo kwimephu yakho ezikhuselekileyo kumntwana wakho ofikisayo? Faka isangqa kuzo\n"
"- Zeziphi iindawo kwimephu yakho ezingakhuselekanga kumntwana wakho ofikisayo? Zihlabe ezo\n"
"- Yintoni eyenza indawo ikhuseleke okanye ingakhuseleki? Ingaba ezi zahlukile kumakhwenkwe namantombazana?\n"
"- Xa ujonga iindawo ozizobele ngaphandle, yeyiphi imigaqo eninokuza nayo kunye ukunceda umntwana wakho ofikisayo ahlale ekhuselekile?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 3: Identify where you can get support."
msgstr "Inyathelo 3: Chonga apho ungafumana inkxaso."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Sometimes, we can find ourselves in trouble.\n"
"\n"
"- Where can you and your teen get support when you face a crisis? MARK those areas with a little object like a stone or piece of paper.\n"
"- Remember your phone and other internet devices. There is a lot of support available online!"
msgstr ""
"Ngamanye amaxesha, singazifumana sisengxakini.\n"
"\n"
"- Wena nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ningayifumana phi inkxaso xa nijamelene negxaki? PHAWULA ezo ndawo ngento encinci enjengelitye okanye iphephatshana.\n"
"- Khumbula ifowuni yakho kunye nezinye izixhobo ze intanethi. Kukho inkxaso eninzi ekhoyo kwi intanethi!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name!
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Now that we understand our safe and unsafe places better, let's look at an example where something simple, like a Safety Word, can help keep your teen safe. \n"
"\n"
"First, think back to when you were a teenager. Was there ever a time when you were in danger but you could not tell your family because they would have been angry?\n"
"\n"
"This ALMOST happened to @data.characters.f1_son_18.name and @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name! Let’s have a look:"
msgstr ""
"Ngoku siyaziqonda ngcono iindawo zethu ezikhuselekileyo nezingakhuselekanga, makhe sijonge umzekelo apho wento elula, njengegama lokhuseleko, inokunceda umntwana wakho ekhuselekile.\n"
"\n"
"Cinga emva ngexesha wawusengumntwana ofikisayo. Lalikhona ixesha apho wawusengozini kodwa wawungakwazi ukuxelela usapho lwakho kuba babezakuba nomsindo?\n"
"\n"
"Lento YAPHANTSE yenzeka ku@data.characters.f1_son_18.name kunye no@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name! makhe sijonge:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Don’t tell the adults, but I am going to a bar with my friends tonight."
msgstr "Ungabaxeleli abantu abadala, kodwa ndiya emzini othengisa utywala nabahlobo bam ebusuku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Have fun! I told them I am staying with my girlfriend, but I am actually going to a cool party."
msgstr "Yonwaba! Ndibaxelele ukuba ndihlala nentombi yam endithandana nayo, kodwa apho ndiya khona ndiya epatini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think they are dealing drugs. We could all get arrested. But I can’t tell my parents – they will be so angry!"
msgstr "Ndicinga ukuba basebenzisa iziyobisi. Singabanjwa sonke. Kodwa andinakubaxelela abazali bam – baya kuba nomsindo kakhulu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am scared. Everyone is too drunk to drive me home. This guy says he will take me, but he wants us to go to his house first. I can’t tell my parents – I lied about coming to this party."
msgstr "Ndiyoyika. Wonke umntu unxile kakhulu ukuba angandigodusa. Lo mfana uthi angandigodusa, kodwa ufuna siqale kwakhe. Andinakubaxelela abazali bam - ndibaxokisele ngokuza kule pati."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "These are dangerous situations! Thankfully, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name and @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name then remembered what their father told them:"
msgstr "Ezi zimeko ezinobungozi! Kungumbulelo, u@data.characters.f1_son_18.name kunye no@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name baye bakhumbula into utata wabo ewayebaxelele yona:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I care about your safety more than anything. If you are ever upset, or scared, you can always call me for help, or tell me about it.\n"
"\n"
"Shall we use an imaginary ‘Aunty Cecilia’ as our Safety Word? Just say something about Aunty Cecilia, I promise that I will try my best to help and I will not be angry – even if you are doing something you shouldn't be doing."
msgstr ""
"Ndiyakhathala ngokhuseleko lwakho ngaphezu kwayo nayiphi into. Ukuba uye wakhathazeka, okanye usoyika, ungandifowunela rhoqo malunga noncedo, okanye undixelele ngalonto. \n"
"\n"
"Singasebenzisa umfanekiso ongengowenyani ka 'kaAunty Cecilia' njengeGama loKhuseleko? Itsho nje into malunga noAunt Cecilia, Ndiyathembisa into yokuba ndizakuzama kangangoko ndinako ukunceda kwaye andizukhathazeka -- noba wenza into ongamelanga ukuba uyayenza."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hey @data.characters.f1_father.role_name, how is Aunty Cecilia doing now?"
msgstr "Hey @data.characters.f1_father.role_name, unjani uAunty Cecilia ngoku?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*(on the other side of the phone)* Not well. We need you at home. I will come pick you up right away. Where are you?"
msgstr "*(Kwelinye icala le phone)* Akukho nto intle. Sidinga wena ekhaya. Ndizazokulanda njengangoku. Uphi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some skills to help you keep your teen safe!"
msgstr "Nazi ezinye izakhono ezingakunceda ukugcina umntwana wakho ofikisayo ekhuselekile!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "MAPS"
msgstr "IIMEPHU"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Make a map with your teen of safe and unsafe areas in your community and online. You and your teen may have different ideas and experiences – try to be open and learn from each other"
msgstr "Yenza i mephu kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo yendawo ezikhuselekileyo kunye nezingakhuselekanga kwindawo ohlala kuyo nakwi intanethi. Wena kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ningaba nengcinga okanye ulwazi olohlukeneyo - zama ukuvuleka kwaye nifunde omnye komnye"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "RULES"
msgstr "IMITHETHO"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Make rules with your teen about how they can stay safe in your community (especially in risky areas that cannot be avoided), and how they can safely use the apps and websites that they like."
msgstr "Yenza imithetho nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ngendlela abanokuhlala ngayo bekhuselekile ekuhlaleni(ingakumbi kwindawo ezingakhuselekanga ongenakuzibaleka), nendlela ekhuselekileyo abangayisebenzisa ekusebenziseni i apps ne webhusayithi abazithandayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Explore with your teen if you can create a rule around sharing with a trusted adult when something feels wrong. This can really help them stay safe in person and online."
msgstr "Phanda kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ukuba ningenza umthetho mayelana nokwabelana nomntu omdala omthembileyo xa kukho into engalunganga. Oku kunokubanceda ngokwenene ukuba bahlale bekhuselekile emntwini nakwi-intanethi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SAFETY WORD"
msgstr "IGAMA LOKHUSELEKO"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Agree on a Safety Word. If something happens that makes your teen upset, uncomfortable or scared, they can say the Safety Word and you will help them without getting angry or punishing them, even if they were doing something wrong."
msgstr "Vumelanani NgeGama loKhuseleko. Ukuba kukho into eyenzekileyo yenza umntwana wakho ofikisayo wakhathazeke, angakhululeki okanye oyike, bangatsho iGama loKhuseleko kwaye ungabanceda ngaphandle kokuba ube nomsindo okanye ubohlwaye, nokuba bebesenza into engalunganga."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Ezinye iingcebiso"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"What Safety Word can you choose with your teen? Here are some ideas from other families:\n"
"\n"
"🥑 A specific food\n"
"👵🏽 A specific family member\n"
"🐒 A specific animal\n"
"🤔 Something else"
msgstr ""
"Leliphi iGama loKhuseleko onolikhetha kunye nomntana wakho ofikisayo? Nantsi eminye imibono esuka kwezinye intsapho.\n"
"\n"
"🥑 Ukutya okuthile\n"
"👵🏽 Ilungu losapho oluthile \n"
"🐒 Isilwanyana esithile\n"
"🤔 Into engenye"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"If you have not done it together yet, this week's home assignment is to make a map with your teen of safe and unsafe places. You can include places from your community 🗺️ and even apps and websites your teen uses online 🌐.\n"
"\n"
"Make sure you are both happy with the safety plan. What really matters is that you talk with your teen as you do this – often teens know much more than we do about where it is safe and unsafe!"
msgstr ""
"Ukuba anikayenzi kunye okwangoku, umsebenzi wasekhaya waleveki kukwenza imephu ezimbini kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ngendawo ezikhuselekileyo nezingakhuselekanga. Ungaquka iindawo ohlala kuyo 🗺️ kunye ne apps okanye i webhusayithi umntwana wakho ofiksayo azisebenzisayo 🌐\n"
"\n"
"Qinisekisa ukuba nobabini nonwabile ngesicwangciso sokhuseleko. Eyona nto ibalulekileyo ngokwenene kukuba uthethe nomntwana wakho ofikisayo njengoko usenza lento – amaxesha amaninzi abantwana abafikisayo basoloko besazi kakhulu kunathi ngendawo ezikhuselekileyo nezi ngakhuselekanga!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you make a safety map with your teen and talk about ways to stay safe online and in your community?"
msgstr "Ungenza imephu ekhuselekileyo nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kwaye nithethe ngeendlela zokuhlala nikhuselekile kwi intanethi nasekuhlaleni?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Taking the time to map out safe and unsafe places together helps your teen feel more confident and supported."
msgstr "Kulungile! Ukuthatha ixesha nisenza imephu zendawo ezikhuselekileyo nezingakhuselekanga kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kwenza azive ezithembile ngakumbi kwaye exhasekile."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Even starting the conversation is a big step towards helping your teen stay safe."
msgstr "Ungayenza! Nokuqala incoko linyathelo elikhulu ukunceda umntwana wakho ofikisayo ahlale ekhuselekile."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. It can feel hard at first, but small talks about safety make a big difference. Try again when you feel ready."
msgstr "Kulungile. Bekunzima ekuqaleni, kodwa lancoko incinci yenza umehluko. Zama kwakhona xa uziva ulungile."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When teens know they can turn to us without fear, they are more likely to ask for help when something feels unsafe - both offline and online. Talking calmly and making safety plans together builds trust that lasts."
msgstr "Xa abantwana abafikisayo besazi bangeza kuthi ngaphandle koloyiko, badla ngokucela uncedo xa besiva into engathi ayikhuselekanga-noba ku kungaphandle kwi intanethi nangaphakathi. Ukuthetha ngomoya ozolileyo nokwenza izicwangciso ezikhuselekileyo kunye nokwakha ukuthembana okungapheliyo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_7.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Safety planning helped @data.characters.media_daughter_7.name open up. Hear her story"
msgstr "Ukucwangisa okukhuselekileyo kuncede u @data.characters.media_daughter_7.name ukuba akhululeke. Yiva ibali lakhe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When my friends or I got into trouble, I would always try to hide it from my mother because she would get so angry and shout at me.\n"
"\n"
"When we made the map of safe and unsafe places, I learnt a lot – also why it is dangerous to share every picture online. My mother told me I can always ask her if there is a problem and she promised she would not get mad.\n"
"\n"
"She kept her promise, so now if I have a problem or I do not feel safe I know we can always come up with a solution together. I can even talk to my mother about the things I do online now!"
msgstr ""
"Xana abahlobo bam okanye umna ndisengxakini, bendiye ndizame ukuyifihla kumama wam ngokuba ebezakuba nomsindo kwaye andingxolise. \n"
"\n"
"Xana sisenza imephu yeendawo ezikhuselekileyo kunye nezingakhuselekanga, ndifunde lukhulu - kwaye kutheni kuyingozi ukwabelana ngomfanekiso ngamnye kwi intanethi. Umama wam wandixelela ukuba ndingakwazi ngalo lonke ixesha ukumbuza ukuba kukhe kwakho ingxaki kwaye wathembisa ukuba akazokucaphuka.\n"
"\n"
"Uye wasigcina isithembiso, ngoku ukuba ndinengxaki okanye andiziva ndikhuselekile ndiyayazi singakwazi ukuza nesisombululo kunye. Ndingakwazi nokuthetha nomama wam malunga nezinto endizenzayo kwi intanethi ngoku!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done for taking time for yourself today. 🎉"
msgstr "Wenze kakuhle ngokuthatha ixesha lesiqu sakho namhlanje. 🎉"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is a short video to help you slow down before you go"
msgstr "Nali ushicilelo olufutshane elizokunceda wehlise ngaphambi kokuba uhambe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When everything feels like it is falling apart And you can't help but raise your voice When all the frustrations are beginning to start Remember that you have a choice\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"You can take pause, you can count to 10 Play a game or do something fun You can phone a friend, someone to confide in Remember you're not the only one\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more Because I really couldn't love you more"
msgstr ""
"Xa yonke into ivakala ingathi iyamoshakala Kwaye awukwazi ukuzinceda uvele unyuse ilizwi Xa zonke iinzingo ziqala Khumbula ukuba ungenza ngakumbi\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sehlise kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Kuba andinakuthanda ngakumbi\n"
"\n"
"Yima, ungabala uyokutsho ku 10 Dlala umdlalo okanye wenze into emnandi Ungafowunela umhlobo, umntu onokumchazela ingxaki Khumbula ayinguwe wedwa\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sime Tsala umoya kancinci Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi \n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsalaa umoya Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sime Tsalaa umoya kancinci Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi"

